OL,3,CWomen beat neighbour to death after
OL,4,Cwrongly accusing him of being a
OL,5,Cpaedophile
OL,7,FTwo women who tortured and beat their
OL,8,F"quiet and shy" neighbour to death
OL,9,Fafter falsely accusing him of being a
OL,10,Fpaedophile, have been convicted of
OL,11,Fmurder.
OL,13,FJurors took just two hours and 35
OL,14,Fminutes to find Zoe Rider, 36, and
OL,15,FNicola Lethbridge, 45, guilty of
OL,16,Fkilling Stephen Koszyczarski.
OL,18,FThe pair filmed some of the "sadistic
OL,19,Fattack" of Mr Koszyczarski at his home
OL,20,Fin on August 9th last year.
