OL,5,Cpaedophile
OL,7,FThe court was shown footage from their
OL,8,Fmobile phones of the killers taunting
OL,9,Fthe 60-year-old while they robbed and
OL,10,Fattacked him.
OL,12,FOn some of the footage, the two women,
OL,13,Fcould be heard hurling sickening abuse
OL,14,Fat a defenceless Mr Koszyczarski.
OL,16,FThe court heard that the women had no
OL,17,Fevidence to prove Mr Koszyczarski was
OL,18,Fa sex offender.
