OL,7,FA South Yorkshire Police investigation
OL,8,Falso uncovered no wrongdoing on his
OL,9,Fpart.
OL,11,FProsecutor Andrew O'Byrne KC told the
OL,12,Fcourt that Mr Koszyczarski lived alone
OL,13,Fat his flat in Fraser Drive, in
OL,14,FWoodseats.
OL,16,FOn the day he died Mr Koszyczarsk had
OL,17,Fgone to a cafe and was having a
OL,18,Fconversation with the woman who owned
OL,19,Fit.
