OL,5,Cpaedophile
OL,7,FHe told her he hadn't been getting
OL,8,Fmuch sleep because people in his block
OL,9,Fwere "making a lot of noise and
OL,10,Fdisturbing him."
OL,12,FCCTV footage captured Mr Koszyczarski
OL,13,Freturning home but at 11.20pm that
OL,14,Fnight he pressed a button activating
OL,15,Fan alarm used for assistance for those
OL,16,Fwith mental health issues.
OL,18,FMr O'Byrne said: "He spoke to an
OL,19,Foperator and asked for assistance. He
OL,20,Ftold them he had been attacked and was
OL,21,Fbleeding."
