OL,7,FIt was said female voices were heard
OL,8,Fin the background of that call.
OL,10,FMr Koszyczarski was taken to hospital
OL,11,Fbut died on August 11. Rider and
OL,12,FLethbridge were arrested and their
OL,13,Fmobile phones seized.
OL,15,FIn a video of the attack found on one
OL,16,Fof the devices, one of the women, was
OL,17,Fwearing cream jogging bottoms.
