OL,7,FForensic examinations later found a
OL,8,Fsmall amount of blood on the joggers
OL,9,Fbelonging to Mr Koszyczarski, with
OL,10,Fboth women's DNA in the waistband of
OL,11,Fthe clothing.
OL,13,FMr O'Byrne said a pathologist who
OL,14,Fcarried out a post-mortem examination
OL,15,Fon Mr Koszyczarski's body said he
OL,16,F"died as a consequence of what he
OL,17,Fdescribes as a sustained and blunt-
OL,18,Fforce physical assault and haemorrhage
OL,19,Fof the skull".
