OL,7,FIt was said Mr Koszyczarski had
OL,8,Finjuries to his head and neck, bruises
OL,9,Fto his ear, eyes, cheeks and lips. He
OL,10,Fhad also suffered bruising to his
OL,11,Fchest that were "most likely caused by
OL,12,Fkicks".
OL,14,FMr O'Byrne described the assault as
OL,15,F"sadistic."
OL,17,FLethbridge and Rider, both of Fraser
OL,18,FDrive, Woodseats, were remanded into
OL,19,Fcustody and will be sentenced on June
OL,20,F5.
