OL,7,FDetective Chief Inspector Tom Woodward
OL,8,Fsaid he was "pleased with the jury's
OL,9,Fverdict."
OL,11,FHe said: "Stephen was described as a
OL,12,Fquiet man. Although he had a close
OL,13,Fcircle of friends, he kept himself to
OL,14,Fhimself and just went about his
OL,15,Fbusiness. He didn't cause any problems
OL,16,For hurt anyone and his death was
OL,17,Fcallous.
